      ],
      "assess": "EEG results indicate brain activity patterns. Select 'Normal' if no epileptiform activity was detected. Choose 'Abnormal' if the EEG showed epileptiform activity, including focal or generalized spikes or spike-and-slow-wave patterns. Select 'Not Done' if the EEG test was not conducted."
    },
    {
